.TH "STX DATA" "1" "2026-04-19" "0.1.0" "stx data Manual"
.SH NAME
stx\-data \- Download and cache market data.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B stx data
[OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Data ingestion: OHLCV fetch and cache layout.
.PP
Subcommands mirror top-level data helpers (e.g. ``stx fetch``).
.PP
.SH COMMANDS
.PP
\fBfetch\fP
  Fetch daily-adjusted OHLCV for symbols...
  See \fBstx data-fetch(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBfetch\fP command.
